@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/agent

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### Send a chat message
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "what is the result of 30 added to 90"
}

### Test empty message (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": ""
}

### Test missing message (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{}